MSqaQ%3D&h=85e8fde2\" target=\"_blank\">http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/74347</a><br />\n<br />\n終極爆陳嘉倩大鑊 前男友認係賤男<br />\n<a href=\"http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/execlusive/1233\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2Fexeclusive%2F1233&d=oJc%2BoIJJC6h83Z5gWO3x3DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6f0318e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/execlusive/1233</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17e3d39a41ef77afb560d5305f5dedf3124d1b9","tid":530764,"uid":144843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fa6a73c545019c29718b9a717fb369649be1527","tid":530764,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:28:55.000Z","msg":"【女神輸曬】陳嘉倩俾前度陳志遠爆 擺明做小三<br />\n<br />\n前大台新聞主播女神，俾網民封為「嘉倩BB」嘅陳嘉倩，因為俾人影到同圈外男友陳志遠拍拖，一段三角關係被揭，屬正印嘅大台藝員朱婉禎鬧佢爭仔，擺明做小三。<br />\n<br />\n事件發展落去，陳嘉倩唔認小三身份，繼而報警話受到滋擾，點知三角關係高潮係，食兩家劈腿男陳志遠企出嚟認係賤男外，亦力証陳嘉倩明知佢有女友，都照舂個頭埋嚟做小三，佢接受訪問時話溝陳嘉倩時，已表明有正印朱婉禎存在，但佢都選擇同佢一齊，仲話佢先係俾人電話滋擾，兼夾座駕俾人損毀，即係受害嗰一個。<br />\n<br />\n做小三，基本上預咗兩敗俱傷嘅下場，仲要撞正個劈腿衰咗擺你上枱嘅男人，呢舖真係輸到底。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180116/568159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180116%2F568159&d=oJc%2BoIJJC6h83Z5gWO3x3DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=3c13ff13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20180116%2F568159&h=7061f44b\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20180116/568159</a>"},{"pid":"ca4a73f81ec3f5c873adc144911eb7689cba6b69","tid":530764,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e17e3d39a41ef77afb560d5305f5dedf3124d1b9","tid":530764,"uid":144843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T06:29:12.000Z",